name: Dafuq? (AudioVisualGans)
description: Trypophobia is an aversion to the sight of irregular patterns or clusters of small holes or bumps. I mean, who likes those to begin with anyways. The visuals were rendered through my original music composition run through LucidSonicDreams. The Trypophobia Dataset compiled by Justin Pinkney is almost unrecognizable at this point, however I like to give credit where credit is due. ///Audio and Visual rendering by Zak Tustont 2021
